    "Resample 0 uses the original train and test split from the UCR archive.",
    "Our primary performance measure is classification accuracy on the test set.",
    "We also compare predictive power with the balanced test set accuracy, to identify whether class imbalance is a problem for an algorithm.",
    "The quality of the probability estimates is measured with the negative log likelihood (NLL), also known as log loss.",
    "The ability to rank predictions is estimated by the area under the receiver operator characteristic curve (AUROC)."
